openmtbmap2img

This script automatically downloads and converts an OpenMTBMap map set to Garmin compatible IMG format.

Usage:

./openmtbmap2img.sh [URL]

where URL is an URL to desired map set, i. e. http://openmtbmap.x-nation.de/maps/mtbdenmark.7z.zip

The Germany map set is used if no command line argument is given.
